      • cooldownStart

        public void cooldownStart()
        Restarts the attack cooldown timer with the previous cooldown value. Note that the cooldown timer is not innately tied to any Tower functionality, so it's up to you to decide what to do with this.

      • cooldownStart

        public void cooldownStart(float seconds)
        Starts the attack cooldown timer and sets it to end after the specified number of seconds. Note that the cooldown timer is not innately tied to any Tower functionality, so it's up to you to decide what to do with this.
        Parameters:
        seconds - How long until the cooldown timer will be ready.
